## 1. CONFIG MANAGER - API AND USAGE

**Location:** `/home/xav/Workspace/Rpstack/redpill/src/ConfigManagerBundle/Model/ConfigManager.php`

**Service Injection:**
```php
use Eliberty\ConfigManagerBundle\Model\ConfigManager;

public function __construct(ConfigManager $configManager) {
    $this->configManager = $configManager;
}
```

**API Methods for Reading Config Keys** (like `booking.v2.tenant-slag`):

| Method | Type | Purpose | Example |
|--------|------|---------|---------|
| `get($key)` | Deprecated | Generic getter | `$this->configManager->get('booking.v2.tenant-slag')` |
| `getStringOption($key, $default)` | String | Fetch string config | `$this->configManager->getStringOption('booking.v2.api-key')` |
| `getIntOption($key, $default)` | Integer | Fetch int config | `$this->configManager->getIntOption('booking.v2.timeout', 30)` |
| `getBoolOption($key, $default)` | Boolean | Fetch boolean config | `$this->configManager->getBoolOption('booking.v2.cache-enabled', true)` |
| `getJsonOption($key, $default)` | JSON/Array | Fetch JSON config | `$this->configManager->getJsonOption('booking.v2.config', [])` |
| `has($key)` | Boolean | Check existence | `if ($this->configManager->has('booking.v2.tenant-slag'))` |
| `getByNamespace($q)` | Array | Get all keys matching prefix | `$this->configManager->getByNamespace('booking.v2.')` |

**Real Example from Codebase:**
```php
// From ElibertyBooking/Rest/ClientFactory.php (line 24-26)
$cfg      = $this->configManager->getByNamespace('booking.guzzle_config');
$username = $this->configManager->getStringOption('booking.wsse_username');
$password = $this->configManager->getStringOption('booking.wsse_password');
```

**Config Key Format:**
- Format: `{group}.{subgroup}.{key}` e.g., `booking.v2.tenant-slag`
- Stored in database, cached in Redis with key: `rp_{env}_{instance}_cfgman`
- TTL: Configured per ConfigurationValue entity

