## 7. SERVICE WIRING & REGISTRATION

### Service Definition Pattern (YAML)

**Primary Config File:** `/home/xav/Workspace/Rpstack/redpill/src/RedpillBundle/Resources/config/services.yml`

### How ExternalActivityHandlers Are Registered

**Auto-Tagging Mechanism:**
```yaml
# Line 185-186 of services.yml
Eliberty\RedpillBundle\ExternalActivity\ExternalActivityHandlerInterface:
    tags: [external_activity.handler]
```

**Compiler Pass:** `/home/xav/Workspace/Rpstack/redpill/src/RedpillBundle/DependencyInjection/Compiler/GenericTagCompilerPass.php` (lines 58, 72-77)

```php
class GenericTagCompilerPass implements CompilerPassInterface {
    public function process(ContainerBuilder $container): void {
        $compilerPassesMapping = [
            // ...
            ExternalActivityHandlerFactory::class => 'external_activity.handler',
        ];

        foreach ($compilerPassesMapping as $factoryServiceId => $tagName) {
            $resolverCollectionDefinition = $container->getDefinition($factoryServiceId);
            foreach ($container->findTaggedServiceIds($tagName) as $serviceId => $tags) {
                $resolverCollectionDefinition->addMethodCall(
                    'add',
                    [new Reference($serviceId), $serviceId]
                );
            }
        }
    }
}
```

### How Handlers Are Retrieved

**Factory Pattern:** `/home/xav/Workspace/Rpstack/redpill/src/RedpillBundle/ExternalActivity/ExternalActivityHandlerFactory.php`

```php
class ExternalActivityHandlerFactory {
    protected array $mapping = [];

    public function add(ExternalActivityHandlerInterface $processor, $serviceId) {
        $this->mapping[$serviceId] = $processor;
    }

    public function getHandler(string $name): ExternalActivityHandlerInterface {
        $serviceId = $this->getServiceId($name);  // Converts "ElibertyBookingV2" to class name
        if (!\array_key_exists($serviceId, $this->mapping)) {
            throw new \UnexpectedValueException(sprintf('ExternalActivity handler not found for %s', $serviceId));
        }
        return $this->mapping[$serviceId];
    }

    private function getServiceId($str): string {
        // Converts "ElibertyBookingV2" to "Eliberty\RedpillBundle\ExternalActivity\ElibertybookingV2\Rest\ElibertybookingV2Handler"
        $str = strtolower($str);
        $str = preg_replace('/[^a-z0-9]+/i', ' ', $str);
        $str = ucwords(trim($str));
        $str = str_replace(' ', '', $str);
        return sprintf('Eliberty\RedpillBundle\ExternalActivity\%s\Rest\%sHandler', $str, $str);
    }
}
```

